rdf:Bag.rdf:li: DNS recursive resolver recurser root nameserver IP address

cc:Work.dc:description: A DNS resolver recursively queries a root nameserver, org. nameserver, and wikipedia.org. nameserver in it's quest to resolve the IP address associated with the domain name www.wikipedia.org. Created and placed into the public domain by myself, Lion Kimbro.
